title: Offseason narratives
itunes:title: Offseason narratives
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- react to the latest NFL news including Ray McDonald's release, Adrian Peterson's situation with the Vikings and Cam Newton's big goals (20:04). The guys then discuss the offseason narratives they don't trust.
